rows.label: qst100203_msg0001
rows.name: That was a heated battle, mo...

rows.label: qst100203_msg0002
rows.name:
After they were beaten and calmed
down, Hiyaya immediately told them
that there was another Delta Box...

rows.label: qst100203_msg0003
rows.name:
They left while complaining,
mo! That was a close call, mo!

rows.label: qst100203_msg0004
rows.name:
The Delta Box is a necessary
material to improve the operating
efficiency of a Divine Beast, mo.

rows.label: qst100203_msg0005
rows.name:
Every country is desperate
to have them live even a
little longer, mo...

rows.label: qst100203_msg0006
rows.name: Thank you for all your help, mo!

rows.label: qst100203_msg0007
rows.name:
Hiyaya will do my best to
stock more in the future, mo.
